name: A Mile A Minute - Original Painting
description: A Mile A Minute Original painting by Ricky Watts Size: 16" x 20" x 1.5" Medium: High quality aerosol paint on gallery stretched canvas Sides are painted and ready to hang or be framed. This piece is signed and dated on the back (See photos for detail). All works are are carefully shipped and delivered via USPS Priority Mail.

name: Mini Series #38 - Original Painting
description: Mini Series #38 Original painting by Ricky Watts Size: 5" x 7" Medium: High quality aerosol paint on stretched canvas Sides are painted and ready to hang or be framed. This piece is signed and dated on the back (See photos for detail). All works are are carefully shipped and delivered via USPS Priority Mail. About the Mini Series paintings: These works are created while I "warm up" for the larger paintings. I make a few at a time to be sure my arm feels good, the paint is flowing and my concentration is dialed in. These are a small piece of a large mural, as if I put the canvas on to the wall and painted over the top of it. Channeling my inner Bob Ross, I often refer to them as children of the larger paintings. I tell them that someday they will grow up to be just like the big creations.
